          </a>
          <a href="https://zenn.dev/yuheiyamada" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"
            class="hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors" aria-label="Zenn">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path
