          </a>
          <a href="mailto:your.email@example.com" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors" aria-label="Email">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path
                d="M20 4H4c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L2 18c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 4l-8 5-8-5V6l8 5 8-5v2z" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-4xl text-center font-semibold mb-12">About Me</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
          <img
            src={profileImageSrc}
            alt="山田祐平の写真"
            class="aspect-square w-full rounded-2xl card-shadow object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">自己紹介</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
              現在、大学でAIを学び、エンタメ領域における業務自動化や研究開発プロジェクトに取り組んでいます。
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              Kaggle Expertとして継続的にアウトプットしつつ、学術・実務の両面からスキルを磨いています。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="education" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-4xl text-center font-semibold mb-4">Education</h2>
        <ol class="relative border-l border-blue-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <li class="mb-10 ml-8">
            <span
              class="absolute -left-3 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-600 ring-4 ring-blue-100"></span>
            <time class="block text-sm text-gray-500">来年（入学予定）</time>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-1">
              <a href="https://www.teu.ac.jp/grad/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"
                class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap">東京工科大学大学院 バイオ・情報メディア研究科 コンピュータサイエンス専攻</a>
            </h3>
          </li>
          <li class="mb-10 ml-8">
            <span
              class="absolute -left-3 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-600 ring-4 ring-blue-100"></span>
            <time class="block text-sm text-gray-500">2023 - now</time>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-1">
              <a href="https://www.teu.ac.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"
                class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors">東京工科大学 コンピュータサイエンス学部 人工知能専攻</a>
            </h3>
          </li>
          <li class="ml-8">
            <span
              class="absolute -left-3 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-600 ring-4 ring-blue-100"></span>
            <time class="block text-sm text-gray-500">2021 - 2023</time>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-1">
              <a href="https://www.neec.ac.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"
                class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors">日本工学院専門学校 ITカレッジ AIシステム科</a>
            </h3>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="experience" class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-4xl text-center font-semibold mb-4">Work Experience</h2>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-4xl text-center font-semibold mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-12">お気軽にお問い合わせください</p>
        <div class="md:flex md:justify-center">
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
            <form class="space-y-6">
              <div>
                <label for="name" class="block mb-2 font-medium">お名前</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required placeholder="山田太郎"
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-600" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label for="email" class="block mb-2 font-medium">メールアドレス</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="your.email@example.com"
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-600" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label for="message" class="block mb-2 font-medium">メッセージ</label>
                <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required placeholder="お問い合わせ内容をご記入ください"
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-600"></textarea>
              </div>
              <button type="submit"
                class="w-full px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors font-medium">
                送信する
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
